This stage is primarily about building the aircraft to deliver the beans. At this stage the aircraft is expected to be able to carry 1 tin of heinz beans. It will have a wingspan of around 2m and have a twin electric motor configuration. This stage will conclude with a flight to drop a tin of beans manualy.

The files in this phase will be based about aircraft design and building and subsequent test flights. In this phase it is also expected to design and build the aviaonics system to essentially fly the plane itself. 
